SUMMARY:Gym Disruption March 26 & 27
DESCRIPTION:We are pleased to announce that Boulderz Etobicoke will be hosting the Ontario Climbing Federation Bouldering B/A/Jr Provincial Competition on March 26 and 27. \nDuring the event\, the Ropes area\, Kids area\, Kilter Board\, and U-Boulder will remain open to members and guests. Weights Area (unavailable March 26 & 27 until 6pm) Please note that portions of the U-Boulder may be temporarily unavailable at certain times throughout the competition. \nThe Competition Wall will be closed from Friday\, March 20 at 9:00 a.m. until Friday\, March 27 at 6:00 p.m. to accommodate route setting and event preparations. \nWe appreciate your understanding and support as we welcome athletes from across Ontario for this exciting event.
URL:https://boulderzclimbing.com/event/gym-disruption-march-26-27/
LOCATION:Etobicoke\, 80 The East Mall Unit 9\, Etobicoke\, Ontario\, M8Z 5X1\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Competition,Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://boulderzclimbing.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/GymDistruption_ProvincialsABJR_website_Athurm_Boulderz2026-1983-x-1571-px-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Boulderz Etobicoke":MAILTO:etobicoke@boulderzclimbing.com
END:VEVENT
