SUMMARY:Shoe Swap 2025-2026
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars! Join us on Sat Mar 28th 10am-3pm  for our Spring Shoe Swap of the season at Boulderz Etobicoke. \nBring your old climbing shoes—no holes\, please—and swap them for another pair. We have sizes available for both kids and adults! \n  \n 
URL:https://boulderzclimbing.com/event/shoe-swap25-26/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:Etobicoke\, 80 The East Mall Unit 9\, Etobicoke\, Ontario\, M8Z 5X1\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://boulderzclimbing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Shoe-Sawp_826_WEB_Eduardo_Boulderz_2025.jpg
END:VEVENT
