SUMMARY:Holiday Hours
DESCRIPTION:Holiday Hours\nFri April 3 & Sun April 5\nFri April 3 \n\n\nEtobicoke 10am-5pm \n\n\nToronto 12pm-5pm \n\n\nMississauga 12pm-5pm \n\n\nSun April 5 \n\n\nEtobicoke 10am-8pm \n\n\nToronto 12pm-5pm \n\n\nMississauga 12pm-5pm \n\n\nSaturday April 4th are regular hours at all locations. \nCome climb with us! 20% discount applied on family admissions\, memberships\, or punch cards.\n(families can be 1 adult with 1-2 kids or 2 adults with 2-4 kids)
URL:https://boulderzclimbing.com/event/holiday-hours/
