SUMMARY:FLASH FRIDAY 2026
DESCRIPTION:FLASH FRIDAY 2026! \nBook the full series & save big! \nIn-house climbing showdown that’s all about fun\, community\, and lots of climbing!\nAll skill levels welcome — this comp is just for fun and friendly competition. \nFLASH FRIDAY 2026 DATES \n\n\nJAN 30 \n\n\nFEB 27 \n\n\nAPRIL 24 \n\n\nMAY 29 \n\n\n\n2026 Pricing\nFlash Friday Events• $17 — Advanced Booking• $25 — Same-Day Booking \nFinale Event• $27 — Advanced Booking• $35 — Same-Day Booking \nFull Series Pass: $70 — Save $8! (Available until Jan 29) \n\nWhat’s in store: \n\n\n15 BRAND NEW problems for each Flash Friday  \n\n\n30 problems lighting up the Finale \n\n\nTons of climbing\, laughs\, and competitive energy \n\n\nEtobicoke Membership\, punch card\, or day admission required (admission included with non-member registration) \nEvent Schedule:\n6–9 PM — Climbing Competition\n9:15 PM — Awards & bragging rights \nCompetition problems are exclusive to registered participants only. \nREGISTER NOW  \nFLASH FRIDAY FEB 27\, 2026 PHOTOS
URL:https://boulderzclimbing.com/event/flash-friday-2026/2026-04-24/
LOCATION:Etobicoke\, 80 The East Mall Unit 9\, Etobicoke\, Ontario\, M8Z 5X1\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Competition,Event
